The paper discusses the progress of artificial intelligence engineering in China, including the development of neural networks, biometric systems, and AI products in companies such as Baidu, Tencent, and Alibaba. These topics are closely related to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
